summary: save game, right out of helgen
descriptionHtml:
this is my new character S\'razirr, he is based off of [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/images/120196]this guy[/url] ,after having help from the guy, who gave me the list of mods he used, and i recreated every aspect. the picture kind of lost some detail because i had to convert it to a gif file. i asked him if i could upload it he said yes, so here it is.
he is level 2 and a vampire, he is straight from helgen, he is in whiterun at the moment, he has 1 perk in light armor.
quests completed: unbound (thats it)
